---------------------------

Bug Fixes:
	I#1441 - itip-formatter: Limit "meeting existence" lookup scope
	I#2911 - Mail: Magic Spacebar sometimes doesn't switch mail
	I#2950 - itip-formatter: Preview calendars' content around the event time
