	EHTMLEditor - Headers and credits are in wrong order when forwarding a message or using the inline reply (Tomas Popela)
	EHTMLEditor - Various fixes when editting the message as new (Tomas Popela)
	EHTMLEditorImageDialog - Don't leak uri variable (Tomas Popela)
	EHRMLEditorImageDialog - Fix the typo and let the Evolution compile again (Tomas Popela)
	EHTMLEditorPageDialog - Remove mistakenly commited debug prints (Tomas Popela)
	EHTMLEditorPageDialog - Don't set transparent background color in Perforated Paper template (Tomas Popela)
	EHTMLEditorSelection - Don't set the alpha channel to 0 (fully transparent) for the default font color (Tomas Popela)
	EHTMLEditorSelection - Try to unref the node when it is set (Tomas Popela)
	EHTMLEditorSelection - Fix the "Wrap Lines" action (Tomas Popela)
	EHTMLEditorSelection - Block format combo box shows wrong format after unblocking the selection-changed signal callback (Tomas Popela)
	EHTMLEditorSelection - Correctly wrap long anchors that are on the beginning of the line in plain text mode (Tomas Popela)
	EHTMLEditorSelection - Fix change of a block format to another one when the citation is selected (Tomas Popela)
	EHTMLEditorSelection - Remove unused variables (Tomas Popela)
	EHTMLEditorSelection - Return correct block node for signature (Tomas Popela)
	EHTMLEditorSelection - Avoid unnecessary wrapping for paragraphs that are wrapped with CSS (Tomas Popela)
	EHTMLEditorView - Sroll to caret when converting the HTML message to the plain text one (Tomas Popela)
	EHTMLEditorView - When switching from HTML mode to the Plain text mode remove all image backgrounds that are set (Tomas Popela)
	EHTMLEditorView - Avoid double citation marks in plain text mode (Tomas Popela)
	EHTMLEditorView - Correctly replace the tab characters with spaces (Tomas Popela)
	EHTMLEditorView - Improve the code that is used for quoting the plain text blocks (Tomas Popela)
	EHTMLEditorView - Correct the logic to get if the body is empty to avoid the unnecessary processing of it (Tomas Popela)
	EHTMLEditorView - Minor refactoring (Tomas Popela)

