	Bug 703244 - Work around GtkBox regression in GTK 3.9.1
	             (Matthew Barnes)
	Bug 703389 - Proxy ignored for images (Milan Crha)
	Bug 703490 - Stop invoking spamc, just use spamassassin
	             (Matthew Barnes)
