	             (Matthew Barnes)
	Bug 647816 - Moving folder hierarchy causes error (David Woodhouse)
	Bug 648308 - Do not display full folder URI in "Opening folder"
	             activity (Dan Vrátil)
	Bug 648317 - MeeGo shell looking for the wrong atom (Abner Silva)
