	  e_import_assistant_new_simple(). (Matthew Barnes)
	* Make EImportAssistant extensible. (Matthew Barnes)
	* addressbook/gui, plugins/groupwise, widgets/misc: Update to new
	  icon theme (Rob Bradford)
