	  (Rob Bradford)
	* Prefer gio-2.0 when requiring GLib libraries. (Matthew Barnes)
	* mail-session: Use the shell's active window as parent for
	  dialog (Rob Bradford)
	* fix lifecycle nasties bgo#625852 (Michael Meeks)

